songs.title: Future
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Yeah
Ahh

[Verse 1]
Hun tattoo meri bahwan te
Police meri rahwan te
Cookies meri ashtray ch
Aish kra main backstage
Meri G-Shock ch time nai
Jine dina da lageya
Ohne dina to hor koi kaim nai
Aine jina naal ladeya
Mere naal ladna hor koi chae nai
Jordans mere pairan ch
Ghumda nave shehran ch
Show kran kamawa lakhan
Ch nai te main kyun kra?
Sikhawan tenu main jiven main peo tera
Industry mere to dardi
Main teretho kyun dra
Ve main teri Kyun suna menu teri lod nai
Soni nachdi jive morni
Lak patla jive MasterCard
No limit menu boldi...

[Chorus]
Hun future meri akhan ch
Bank accounts mere lakhan ch
Hun dekhya jo sapneya ch
Leh ke firda main hatha ch...
Hun future meri akhan ch
Bank accounts mere lakhan ch
Hun dekhya jo sapneya ch
Leh ke firda main hatha ch...

[Verse 2]
Gucci belt Versace shades
Tere saal di kamai mere ek show da rate
Tera nwa cha rap mere vaste khed
Nwi CD nwa rate album late
Bandi gal munde karde rap
Yaar ande bhar pela torke oh soch di kaid
Choti soch gallan wadiyaan
Video ch rental gaddiyaan
Main dsa HipHop ki?
Anne note kamaye
Hun dhup jdo aye
Nwi gaddi vich Ray-Bans paye
Jdo ghumman jaye mere Daddy Ji
Main dsa HipHop ki?
California di daliyan ch choti ji umar ton apan
Zindigi bitai keve torde Swisher Sweets...

[Chorus]
Hun future meri akhan ch
Bank accounts mere lakhan ch
Hun dekhya jo sapneya ch
Leh ke firda main hatha ch...
Hun future meri akhan ch
Bank accounts mere lakhan ch
Hun dekhya jo sapneya ch
Leh ke firda main hatha ch
